    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine domini Dei salvatoris Ihesu Christi. Concessimus nos vir
                        gloriosissimus <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/90"
                            >Waimarius</persName> Dei prebidentia langobardorum gentis <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>
                        <rs key="#Intercessory">per postulationem</rs> domne <persName
                            ref="#people/3695" key="#Principissa">Landelaiche</persName> matris mee
                        in <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Private_foundations" ref="#juridical_persons/77"
                            >Sancti Maximi</orgName>, quod domnus <persName key="#Princeps"
                            ref="#people/3694">Waiferius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> pater meus intus, hec cibitate Salerno a
                        nobo construxit fundamine, integram rebus <name ref="Benenatus"
                            >Benenati</name> et <name ref="Ademarius">Ademari</name> omnia illorum
                        pertinentia, ubique exinde fuerit inbentus, eo quod <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Inheritance #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >sine heredes mortui sunt</rs> et sacri nostri palatii pertinet de loco
                        supter ipsa fistula, ubi propio Puteo regente bocatur <placeName
                            ref="#places/4014"
                            key="#Cities #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Inheritance #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >Nucerina</placeName> fines et pertinet de<rs key="#Actio"> acto</rs>
                        salernitano, in ea bidelicet ratione, ut ammodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum
                        roboreum preceptum cungta ea, que supra legitur, in eadem sanctam sedem
                        permaneat eius rectoribus dominandum in perpetuum, et a nullo ex nostris
                        iudicibus, idest comitibus, gastaldeis, bel a quibuscumque agentibus numquam
                        abeat aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetui tempore in supradicta sancta
                        ecclesia permaneat. Quod vero preceptum concessionis ex iussione
                        suprascripte potestati scripsit ego (+) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"
                            ref="#people/4477">Dausdedi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/84"
                            key="#Cities">Salerno</placeName> decimo anno mense magius quarta
                        indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
